net.sf.sprockets.google

Class ImmutableReview.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.sprockets.google.ImmutableReview.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    ImmutableReview

    @NotThreadSafe
public static final class ImmutableReview.Builder
extends Object
    Builds instances of ImmutableReview. Initialize attributes and then invoke build() method to create immutable instance.

    Builder is not thread safe and generally should not be stored in field or collection, but used immediately to create instances.

        public final ImmutableReview.Builder from(Place.Review instance)
        Fill builder with attribute values from provided Place.Review instance. Regular attribute values will be replaced with ones of an instance. Instance's absent optional values will not replace present values. Collection elements and entries will be added, not replaced.
